WEBVTT

00:01:40.650 --> 00:01:45.950
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

00:01:45.990 --> 00:01:48.950
[Episode 12]

00:01:58.550 --> 00:01:59.200
Ladies,

00:01:59.200 --> 00:01:59.509
[2024 Nuanhai E-commerce Product
Selection Sharing Conference]

00:01:59.509 --> 00:02:01.240
let's start picking products.

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:02.430
Hua isn't here yet—

00:02:02.430 --> 00:02:03.200
should we wait for her?

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:04.070
No need.

00:02:04.070 --> 00:02:05.130
Let's start first.

00:02:05.180 --> 00:02:06.990
If we finish early, we can go eat.

00:02:07.150 --> 00:02:07.640
Okay.

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:09.039
Let's look at mine first.

00:02:09.240 --> 00:02:10.430
This serum

00:02:10.449 --> 00:02:12.580
is really effective for fading spots—

00:02:12.840 --> 00:02:15.120
the only downside is that it's expensive.

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:17.150
Your target customers are all young girls.

00:02:17.150 --> 00:02:18.210
Can they afford it?

00:02:19.590 --> 00:02:21.000
I've got a budget-friendly one here.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:21.720
Take a look.

00:02:24.890 --> 00:02:25.980
With these ingredients,

00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:27.360
you'll definitely get sued.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:29.190
You'll lose a fortune in compensation.

00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:30.520
Mine uses healthy,

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:31.750
natural herbal extracts—

00:02:31.750 --> 00:02:32.840
absolutely safe—

00:02:32.840 --> 00:02:34.400
and the price is affordable too.

00:02:34.400 --> 00:02:35.840
I've been using it
for over two months now,

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:37.120
and I have sensitive skin.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:39.810
I didn't get any allergies
even during the seasonal change this year.

00:02:39.810 --> 00:02:41.870
It's made with natural ingredients.

00:02:42.150 --> 00:02:43.310
Why does your face

00:02:43.990 --> 00:02:46.590
look more and more yellow
the longer you use it?

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:48.640
That won't do.

00:02:49.910 --> 00:02:50.970
Actually, ladies,

00:02:51.079 --> 00:02:51.870
I just got

00:02:52.430 --> 00:02:53.360
a new batch of products in.

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:55.020
They're selling really well.

00:02:55.150 --> 00:02:56.710
But I was thinking—

00:02:56.710 --> 00:02:58.890
if there's money to be made,
we should make it together.

00:02:58.890 --> 00:03:01.450
I'm currently a provincial-level agent,

00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:03.750
and I'm honestly too busy
to handle everything.

00:03:03.750 --> 00:03:06.410
Is anyone interested in
becoming my sub-agent?

00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:07.190
What brand is it?

00:03:07.190 --> 00:03:08.250
Is it that popular?

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:11.300
Is it the essence mask you've been selling
on your Moments?

00:03:11.300 --> 00:03:12.020
Hong.

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:13.150
You've all heard of

00:03:13.170 --> 00:03:14.290
Hong from Hainan, right?

00:03:14.290 --> 00:03:16.430
The factories she works with are solid.

00:03:16.430 --> 00:03:17.240
That batch of products she picked

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:19.490
has already sold out like crazy in Hainan.

00:03:19.490 --> 00:03:21.840
Her sheet masks really sell that well?

00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:23.079
Of course.

00:03:23.079 --> 00:03:24.000
What kind of margins are we talking about?

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:24.750
How much can we actually make?

00:03:24.750 --> 00:03:25.430
Sorry.

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:26.950
Sorry, ladies.

00:03:27.910 --> 00:03:28.520
Hua.

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:30.840
I was chatting with some business owners

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:31.630
from the city around noon

00:03:31.630 --> 00:03:33.360
and totally lost track of time.

00:03:33.630 --> 00:03:35.360
What are you all talking about?

00:03:35.550 --> 00:03:36.630
Xiaoya just said

00:03:36.630 --> 00:03:38.140
she wants to share
a money-making opportunity

00:03:38.140 --> 00:03:39.000
with everyone.

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:42.440
Wow, that generous, huh?

00:03:42.910 --> 00:03:43.860
Of course.

00:03:44.490 --> 00:03:45.610
I, Li Xiaoya,

00:03:45.640 --> 00:03:47.170
have always believed that
if there's money to be made,

00:03:47.170 --> 00:03:48.600
we all make it together—

00:03:49.180 --> 00:03:50.200
unlike some people

00:03:50.200 --> 00:03:51.360
who are so cheap

00:03:51.510 --> 00:03:53.720
you can't get a dime out of them.

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:55.120
Is that so?

00:03:55.710 --> 00:03:58.710
You actually want to
share the profits with everyone?

00:03:59.520 --> 00:04:01.680
This "money-making opportunity"

00:04:01.870 --> 00:04:05.010
wouldn't happen to be the sheet masks
you're selling right now, would it?

00:04:05.010 --> 00:04:06.060
Yeah, it's that one.

00:04:06.060 --> 00:04:08.570
Xiaoya said she got the stock from Hong.

00:04:09.190 --> 00:04:10.790
So it really is this product.

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:13.640
I was just talking about it
with some business people earlier.

00:04:13.640 --> 00:04:15.080
You guys seriously don't know?

00:04:15.080 --> 00:04:15.940
What happened?

00:04:16.100 --> 00:04:17.130
So Hong's scandal

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:18.209
blew up.

00:04:19.350 --> 00:04:22.160
All those sales numbers
she'd been bragging about

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:24.110
were fake.

00:04:24.290 --> 00:04:25.430
Now distributors and agents

00:04:25.430 --> 00:04:26.870
from all over the country

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:29.520
have gone to Hainan
to demand their money back.

00:04:29.790 --> 00:04:31.550
Honestly, she's something else.

00:04:31.550 --> 00:04:33.190
She took the payments

00:04:33.900 --> 00:04:35.159
and ran a long time ago.

00:04:36.190 --> 00:04:37.020
That's ridiculous.

00:04:37.020 --> 00:04:37.730
By the way,

00:04:37.870 --> 00:04:38.840
Xiaoya,

00:04:39.170 --> 00:04:42.200
you must have heard about
this way earlier.

00:04:43.760 --> 00:04:45.290
Why didn't you go to Hainan?

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:47.760
See,

00:04:47.830 --> 00:04:49.870
Xiaoya's the smart one.

00:04:50.420 --> 00:04:52.060
What's the point of going to Hainan?

00:04:52.060 --> 00:04:53.830
You can't get their money back anyway.

00:04:53.830 --> 00:04:55.280
Might as well stay here

00:04:55.310 --> 00:04:56.780
and rope a few people in

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:59.360
to help share the losses,

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:00.190
right?

00:05:00.550 --> 00:05:01.230
Xiaoya,

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:02.910
that's really shady of you!

00:05:08.440 --> 00:05:10.590
Don't listen to her nonsense.

00:05:11.390 --> 00:05:12.680
I had no idea about

00:05:12.700 --> 00:05:13.780
Hong's scandal.

00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:15.720
Whatever's going on with her
has nothing to do with me.

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:18.430
The product is still selling
just fine on my end.

00:05:20.070 --> 00:05:21.130
So are you in or not?

00:05:24.070 --> 00:05:25.190
If not, forget it.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:27.000
It's totally voluntary.

00:05:27.670 --> 00:05:29.000
I'm not forcing anyone.

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:30.360
Li Xiaoya,

00:05:30.650 --> 00:05:32.180
I don't usually admit this,

00:05:32.230 --> 00:05:34.080
but I gotta hand it to you—

00:05:34.310 --> 00:05:35.630
your mouth is sharp.

00:05:37.310 --> 00:05:39.680
Has it really been six, seven years

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.230
since we met at the county radio station?

00:05:41.230 --> 00:05:42.840
We're old friends.

00:05:43.100 --> 00:05:45.690
Who doesn't lose a little money
in business?

00:05:46.170 --> 00:05:47.850
Listen, as your older sister,

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:49.680
I gotta say—

00:05:49.700 --> 00:05:52.260
you've got zero talent for this.

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.640
Just go home, take it easy,

00:05:54.900 --> 00:05:57.340
and stop piling up debt.

00:06:01.690 --> 00:06:02.890
I didn't even bring up

00:06:02.950 --> 00:06:03.830
all the messy stuff she did before

00:06:03.830 --> 00:06:05.290
just to give her some face.

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:05.920
Come on.

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:07.180
Let's not talk about her.

00:06:07.180 --> 00:06:08.310
Let's talk about us.

00:07:02.200 --> 00:07:03.460
I'm going downstairs.

00:07:07.750 --> 00:07:09.080
What are you doing here?

00:07:11.620 --> 00:07:13.480
I just finished dinner with some friends.

00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:14.280
What's wrong?

00:07:14.630 --> 00:07:15.380
Nothing.

00:07:15.600 --> 00:07:16.530
Why are you here?

00:07:17.070 --> 00:07:18.070
We're here to report on work.

00:07:18.070 --> 00:07:19.730
We'll head back after eating.

00:07:19.830 --> 00:07:20.870
I won't keep you company today then.

00:07:20.870 --> 00:07:21.560
I have things to do at home.

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:22.490
I'm leaving now.

00:07:22.510 --> 00:07:23.200
Is everything really okay?

00:07:23.200 --> 00:07:24.120
I'm fine.

00:07:24.380 --> 00:07:25.510
What could be wrong?

00:07:25.990 --> 00:07:26.720
Go ahead. Drive safe.

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:27.870
Take care.

00:07:28.630 --> 00:07:28.950
Bye.

00:07:28.970 --> 00:07:29.530
Bye.

00:07:33.980 --> 00:07:35.450
What a loser.

00:07:36.159 --> 00:07:38.360
Always pretending to be rich every day.

00:07:38.909 --> 00:07:41.240
Bet you're hanging onto some idiot again.

00:07:42.700 --> 00:07:43.960
Who are you cursing at?

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:45.560
Who are you?

00:07:45.560 --> 00:07:46.190
I'm nobody.

00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:46.720
I just heard you cussing someone

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:47.430
and wanted to cuss you back.

00:07:47.430 --> 00:07:48.120
What's she done to you?

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:48.680
Go on.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:49.159
What did she do to you?

00:07:49.159 --> 00:07:49.680
Try saying one more word.

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:50.580
Who are you calling a loser?

00:07:50.580 --> 00:07:51.159
Who are you calling a loser?

00:07:51.159 --> 00:07:51.630
I said it.

00:07:51.630 --> 00:07:52.070
What do you mean by loser?

00:07:52.070 --> 00:07:52.430
I said it. So what?

00:07:52.430 --> 00:07:53.870
What does it have to do with you?

00:07:53.870 --> 00:07:54.630
Okay, okay, lady.

00:07:54.630 --> 00:07:55.720
Get in the car.

00:07:55.870 --> 00:07:56.830
Seriously.

00:07:57.650 --> 00:07:58.409
Crazy.

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:25.270
Eat.

00:08:26.270 --> 00:08:27.660
We have work to do when we get back.

00:08:27.660 --> 00:08:28.310
I'm full.

00:08:28.310 --> 00:08:29.570
Finish up and let's go.

00:08:34.539 --> 00:08:35.850
The Hu Wenjing I know,

00:08:36.150 --> 00:08:37.870
is calm, rational,

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:38.850
and professional.

00:08:38.850 --> 00:08:40.200
What's wrong with you today?

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:41.030
Who is this person you know?

00:08:41.030 --> 00:08:42.200
Introduce me to her.

00:08:54.910 --> 00:08:56.510
I know what's bothering you.

00:08:59.200 --> 00:09:00.400
But you shouldn't be upset now.

00:09:00.400 --> 00:09:01.910
If you hadn't doubted back then,
you wouldn't be feeling this way.

00:09:01.910 --> 00:09:02.670
And since you did doubt,

00:09:02.670 --> 00:09:04.530
you have no reason to be upset now.

00:09:08.030 --> 00:09:09.030
I shouldn't have doubted her.

00:09:09.030 --> 00:09:10.500
I've known her my whole life.

00:09:10.500 --> 00:09:11.340
Now I don't

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:13.440
even know what to think.

00:09:17.470 --> 00:09:18.110
Look.

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:19.840
Let's put it this way.

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:20.700
You're the boss here,

00:09:20.700 --> 00:09:21.830
so I won't go on about

00:09:22.400 --> 00:09:24.260
how everything should be doubted.

00:09:24.260 --> 00:09:25.190
I'm just saying:

00:09:25.300 --> 00:09:26.500
if my dad's a suspect,

00:09:26.670 --> 00:09:27.720
I'll investigate.

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:28.790
If he breaks the law,

00:09:28.790 --> 00:09:29.320
I'll arrest him.

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:30.450
And if it's your mom,

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:39.010
I'll stay out of it
to avoid any conflict of interest.

00:09:45.280 --> 00:09:47.220
[Li Xiaoya]

00:09:52.450 --> 00:09:53.670
[Voice Call]

00:10:02.230 --> 00:10:03.550
Call her if you want.

00:10:03.790 --> 00:10:05.120
Say whatever you want to say.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:06.650
Don't beat around the bush.

00:10:19.320 --> 00:10:20.320
I just wanted to check:

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:22.200
you rushed off just now.

00:10:23.180 --> 00:10:24.310
Is everything okay?

00:10:24.630 --> 00:10:25.470
I'm fine.

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:28.010
It's just a small business hiccup,

00:10:28.310 --> 00:10:29.360
easy to fix.

00:10:30.490 --> 00:10:31.380
Scold me?

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:33.820
That's normal.

00:10:33.850 --> 00:10:34.980
She's just jealous.

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:36.670
I'm really fine.

00:10:36.750 --> 00:10:38.350
Why would I be angry with her?

00:10:39.340 --> 00:10:40.270
I'm not short of money—

00:10:40.270 --> 00:10:41.720
if I am, I'd come to you.

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:42.510
okay?

00:10:43.670 --> 00:10:44.680
Don't work too hard.

00:10:44.680 --> 00:10:45.940
Take care of yourself.

00:10:47.210 --> 00:10:47.940
Don't worry.

00:10:48.010 --> 00:10:49.540
Let's hang out another day.

00:11:03.230 --> 00:11:03.840
Go on.

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:45.960
It's pitch black.

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:47.820
Why didn't you turn on the lights?

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:53.990
You poor thing.

00:11:54.020 --> 00:11:56.150
You're eating instant noodles again?

00:11:58.610 --> 00:12:01.470
You're getting caught up
in research and spy stuff?

00:12:05.490 --> 00:12:07.750
Do you think I'll ever succeed in my life?

00:12:09.030 --> 00:12:11.580
That depends on
what you mean by "success."

00:12:14.660 --> 00:12:16.130
I mean making a name for myself

00:12:16.130 --> 00:12:17.330
and making big money.

00:12:18.790 --> 00:12:20.120
You know, in this world,

00:12:21.280 --> 00:12:23.480
there are a lot of people with big dreams

00:12:23.750 --> 00:12:24.910
but fragile luck.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:28.270
Often, it's because they lack ability.

00:12:28.270 --> 00:12:29.330
But that's not you.

00:12:29.670 --> 00:12:31.400
You're just unlucky this time.

00:12:34.730 --> 00:12:36.790
Don't bother sugarcoating it for me.

00:12:37.310 --> 00:12:38.190
I'm not.

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:40.390
I believe in you.

00:12:40.390 --> 00:12:42.050
You will definitely succeed.

00:12:53.510 --> 00:12:54.510
Round and round…

00:12:55.920 --> 00:12:57.690
I never thought the person
who believes in me the most

00:12:57.690 --> 00:12:59.090
would be right beside me.

00:12:59.670 --> 00:13:00.730
I always have been.

00:13:01.970 --> 00:13:04.030
Why are you suddenly telling me this?

00:13:06.470 --> 00:13:07.730
I went to see Cheng Ken.

00:13:08.870 --> 00:13:09.670
Li Xiaoya,

00:13:10.760 --> 00:13:12.090
are you out of your mind?

00:13:12.160 --> 00:13:13.120
Snap out of it!

00:13:13.670 --> 00:13:15.600
Dealing drugs will get you killed!

00:13:15.910 --> 00:13:16.870
I knew you'd get tempted—

00:13:16.870 --> 00:13:17.750
I shouldn't have told you!

00:13:17.750 --> 00:13:18.680
I'm telling you,

00:13:21.430 --> 00:13:23.690
I've spent all the money Ding Lai gave us.

00:13:23.740 --> 00:13:24.960
If we don't figure something out,

00:13:24.960 --> 00:13:26.520
the rest of our lives are over.

00:13:26.520 --> 00:13:28.460
What's more important, money or your life?

00:13:28.460 --> 00:13:29.740
You're blinded by cash.

00:13:29.740 --> 00:13:31.830
Don't you have to pay with your life
if you kill someone?

00:13:31.830 --> 00:13:34.630
Can you guarantee the police
will never catch you?

00:13:34.670 --> 00:13:36.470
Do you want to spend the rest of our lives

00:13:36.470 --> 00:13:39.480
worrying about poverty?

00:13:45.950 --> 00:13:47.120
I've made up my mind.

00:13:47.820 --> 00:13:49.460
We'll do it the way

00:13:50.530 --> 00:13:51.840
Ding Lai planned

00:13:54.380 --> 00:13:55.840
and pull off one big score.

00:13:56.210 --> 00:13:57.740
Once it's done, we're gone.

00:14:00.120 --> 00:14:00.510
Gone?

00:14:00.530 --> 00:14:01.320
Where to?

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:02.910
Go abroad.

00:14:04.180 --> 00:14:05.110
The two of us.

00:14:13.020 --> 00:14:15.380
We can leave your mom

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:16.770
a lot of money—

00:14:17.950 --> 00:14:19.710
enough for the rest of her life.

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:30.770
Didn't you say you were ready?

00:14:34.190 --> 00:14:36.050
Didn't you say you'd listen to me?

00:14:38.830 --> 00:14:40.200
Once we leave, there's no coming back.

00:14:40.200 --> 00:14:41.050
I don't care.

00:14:42.670 --> 00:14:44.800
There's nothing here I'm attached to.

00:14:56.440 --> 00:14:57.800
Cheng Ken is a good man.

00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:00.540
But he's not smart.

00:15:02.360 --> 00:15:04.490
Working with him is definitely risky.

00:15:04.900 --> 00:15:06.700
I'm already trafficking drugs.

00:15:07.670 --> 00:15:09.330
Why would I be afraid of risks?

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:14.160
But you're right.

00:15:17.390 --> 00:15:18.510
In this matter,

00:15:20.450 --> 00:15:21.380
we must have

00:15:22.180 --> 00:15:23.140
the initiative.

00:15:40.150 --> 00:15:41.910
Xiaoyu, if you're scared,

00:15:41.910 --> 00:15:43.550
just think of it as Jiajia.

00:15:43.830 --> 00:15:45.870
I'll be with you the whole time.

00:15:51.470 --> 00:15:52.360
Dad.

00:15:52.980 --> 00:15:54.180
The oven.

00:16:04.750 --> 00:16:05.510
From now on,

00:16:06.520 --> 00:16:08.520
you can't eat milk tablets anymore.

00:16:08.680 --> 00:16:10.960
If there's even one in the house,

00:16:11.590 --> 00:16:12.650
you can't touch it.

00:16:13.570 --> 00:16:14.240
Got it?

00:16:14.830 --> 00:16:16.750
I can give up the milk tablets,

00:16:17.030 --> 00:16:19.400
but I'll miss Xiaoyu.

00:16:24.160 --> 00:16:24.830
I know.

00:16:27.040 --> 00:16:28.260
You'll see each other again.

00:16:28.260 --> 00:16:29.190
I promise,

00:16:30.420 --> 00:16:33.020
once I finish everything
I've got going on,

00:16:33.300 --> 00:16:34.690
I'll let you meet.

00:16:35.750 --> 00:16:36.630
When I have time,

00:16:36.630 --> 00:16:38.390
I'll even learn a new skill

00:16:38.850 --> 00:16:40.660
so I can bake little fish cookies

00:16:41.590 --> 00:16:42.650
for you and Xiaoyu.

