Say goodbye to Xiaoyu.

00:17:06.440 --> 00:17:08.230
Bye, Xiaoyu.

00:17:12.960 --> 00:17:13.960
Xiaoyu, let's go.

00:17:16.220 --> 00:17:17.079
Let's head out.

