00:19:16.830 --> 00:19:18.490
Sorry to trouble you, Auntie.

00:19:20.970 --> 00:19:23.170
This house belonged to my grandmother.

00:19:23.770 --> 00:19:24.960
After she passed away,

00:19:24.960 --> 00:19:25.950
