00:19:25.950 --> 00:19:27.210
and my mom gave it to me.

00:19:27.480 --> 00:19:28.070
Auntie

00:19:28.230 --> 00:19:29.230
lives over there.

00:19:29.720 --> 00:19:31.780
She usually takes care of this house.

00:19:39.740 --> 00:19:41.580
Auntie keeps this place pretty clean.

00:19:41.580 --> 00:19:42.910
She cleans it every day.

00:19:49.720 --> 00:19:50.840
There's a room upstairs

00:19:50.840 --> 00:19:51.830
she can sleep in.

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:08.830
Does Ken

00:20:09.500 --> 00:20:11.950
