00:20:12.360 --> 00:20:13.360
or a young wife?

00:20:13.850 --> 00:20:15.380
My brother's heart is pure.

00:20:19.730 --> 00:20:20.490
How is it?

00:20:20.690 --> 00:20:21.650
Not bad, right?

00:20:22.670 --> 00:20:23.470
Alright then.

00:20:23.520 --> 00:20:24.270
Let's go.

00:20:24.440 --> 00:20:26.170
I'll go have a word with Auntie.

00:20:26.190 --> 00:20:27.390
You guys get settled.

00:20:27.550 --> 00:20:28.350
Wait a minute.

00:20:28.580 --> 00:20:29.380
Wait a minute.

00:20:33.550 --> 00:20:34.750
This is

00:20:35.110 --> 00:20:36.820
the starting point of our partnership.

00:20:36.820 --> 00:20:39.420
There are many things
we need to clarify today.

00:20:44.790 --> 00:20:45.270
Sit.

00:21:05.060 --> 00:21:05.780
First,

00:21:06.440 --> 00:21:07.970
I need to stress something:

00:21:09.640 --> 00:21:10.720
