00:21:10.720 --> 00:21:12.520
is a life-or-death deal.

00:21:15.130 --> 00:21:15.930
The three of us

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:17.740
have to stick together

00:21:20.110 --> 00:21:22.030
and follow my plan to the letter.

00:21:23.960 --> 00:21:24.470
Second...

00:21:24.470 --> 00:21:25.510
Second what?

00:21:25.740 --> 00:21:27.940
I don't even agree with the first point.

00:21:28.550 --> 00:21:30.940
What do you mean
"follow your plan to the letter"?

00:21:30.940 --> 00:21:32.010
