00:21:32.430 --> 00:21:33.310
Is it detailed? Thought out?

00:21:33.310 --> 00:21:34.440
Guaranteed to work?

00:21:34.550 --> 00:21:36.410
Have you ever dealt drugs before?

00:21:36.750 --> 00:21:38.360
Or have you ever met a drug dealer?

00:21:38.360 --> 00:21:39.230
Have you?

00:21:45.650 --> 00:21:46.610
Well, no.

00:21:48.040 --> 00:21:49.570
We are all ordinary people.

00:21:50.410 --> 00:21:52.270
We don't understand this circle.

00:21:53.070 --> 00:21:55.160
And I've already proven with my actions

00:21:55.160 --> 00:21:57.020
that we can't even get close to it.

00:21:58.470 --> 00:21:58.990
But

00:22:00.360 --> 00:22:02.510
that's a mindset problem.

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:05.370
Who says drugs have to be sold to addicts?

00:22:05.990 --> 00:22:07.600
When you sell a product,

00:22:07.960 --> 00:22:09.360
