00:22:09.750 --> 00:22:10.750
who have a demand.

00:22:11.370 --> 00:22:13.170
What we're selling isn't drugs.

00:22:13.670 --> 00:22:16.680
It's a diet pill that doesn't exist
anywhere else on the market.

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:18.760
Drugs are sold to addicts.

00:22:18.790 --> 00:22:20.710
Diet pills are sold to people
who want to lose weight.

00:22:20.710 --> 00:22:22.090
Addicts are hard to find.

00:22:22.090 --> 00:22:25.150
People who want to lose weight
are everywhere you look.

00:22:28.960 --> 00:22:29.610
Not bad.

00:22:30.360 --> 00:22:31.120
Very good.

00:22:33.230 --> 00:22:34.690
I think your idea is great.

00:22:36.030 --> 00:22:36.830
I admit that,

00:22:37.170 --> 00:22:38.370
but it lacks details.

00:22:38.720 --> 00:22:40.240
How exactly are we going to pull it off?

00:22:40.240 --> 00:22:41.710
Do you know where these goods

00:22:41.710 --> 00:22:42.600
are produced?

00:22:42.870 --> 00:22:44.000
How to package them?

00:22:44.150 --> 00:22:45.150
How do we operate?

00:22:45.790 --> 00:22:46.880
How to market them?

00:22:47.230 --> 00:22:48.300
How do we get people to buy them?

00:22:48.300 --> 00:22:49.230
How to ship them?

00:22:53.490 --> 00:22:55.620
That's the part you need to figure out.

00:22:55.750 --> 00:22:56.910
I provide the supply

00:22:57.030 --> 00:22:58.150
and the strategic direction.

00:22:58.150 --> 00:23:00.130
You've only provided
the supply and direction,

00:23:00.130 --> 00:23:00.960
but I'm

00:23:01.860 --> 00:23:04.970
the one who's going to execute

00:23:05.710 --> 00:23:07.440
and shape the whole operation,

00:23:08.570 --> 00:23:09.920
so you should be listening to me.

00:23:09.920 --> 00:23:12.110
I put my life and my daughter's life

00:23:12.110 --> 00:23:13.310
in your hands.

00:23:13.690 --> 00:23:14.410
Is that ridiculous?

00:23:14.410 --> 00:23:16.480
Then isn't it just as ridiculous

00:23:16.920 --> 00:23:19.460
