00:24:12.100 --> 00:24:12.860
Impossible.

00:24:13.470 --> 00:24:14.550
Are you kidding me?

00:24:14.900 --> 00:24:16.450
I'm the one selling the goods.

00:24:16.450 --> 00:24:18.370
I take the highest risk.

00:24:18.750 --> 00:24:20.750
Why should you get the lion's share?

00:24:21.780 --> 00:24:22.440
