00:24:29.360 --> 00:24:30.760
Can you two stop arguing?

00:24:38.810 --> 00:24:40.350
I don't want a share anymore.

00:24:40.350 --> 00:24:41.810
You split it fifty-fifty.

00:24:42.310 --> 00:24:43.910
Xiaoya knows business best,

00:24:44.750 --> 00:24:45.810
so you handle that side.

00:24:45.810 --> 00:24:46.870
You keep the books.

00:24:50.160 --> 00:24:52.220
I'll handle counter-surveillance.

00:24:52.530 --> 00:24:53.910
You two fill in the gaps.

00:24:54.990 --> 00:24:55.550
Ken,

00:24:56.350 --> 00:24:57.880
