00:24:58.760 --> 00:25:00.020
but there's one thing.

00:25:00.560 --> 00:25:02.660
You've got to stop chewing that stuff.

00:25:02.660 --> 00:25:03.510
You must quit.

00:25:03.720 --> 00:25:04.850
If you keep doing it,

00:25:05.120 --> 00:25:06.070
