00:27:04.070 --> 00:27:06.870
Most of my clients on social media
are young women.

00:27:07.270 --> 00:27:09.480
They have a huge demand for weight loss.

00:27:10.210 --> 00:27:11.590
Our costs are very low,

00:27:11.880 --> 00:27:13.680
so we can let them try it for free.

00:27:56.680 --> 00:27:58.200
We need to lower the ratio

00:27:58.750 --> 00:28:01.240
and stick to the method you used
for the milk tablets before—

00:28:01.240 --> 00:28:02.170
