00:29:58.930 --> 00:30:00.090
Let's hurry up.

00:30:11.880 --> 00:30:12.720
Zhang Yan said,

00:30:12.720 --> 00:30:14.440
Cao Jinchuan didn't make it to Xiamen.

00:30:14.440 --> 00:30:16.880
He got off at a small station
called Tuzhou.

00:30:16.880 --> 00:30:19.100
Then he stole a bike there,

00:30:19.130 --> 00:30:20.620
and rode it back to Nuanfeng County.

00:30:20.620 --> 00:30:23.020
Can you believe he pedaled
all the way back?

00:30:23.170 --> 00:30:24.760
He's got a lot of nerve.

00:30:25.480 --> 00:30:26.640
Does he think the most dangerous place

00:30:26.640 --> 00:30:27.550
