00:30:45.880 --> 00:30:46.680
What is it?

00:30:46.950 --> 00:30:48.220
Come outside with me.

00:30:49.130 --> 00:30:49.890
Follow me.

00:30:55.890 --> 00:30:56.280
Go.

00:30:56.310 --> 00:30:56.640
Go in!

00:31:37.180 --> 00:31:38.510
Who are you looking for?

00:31:38.590 --> 00:31:39.200
Hello.

00:31:39.220 --> 00:31:40.770
Is Cao Jinchuan here?

00:31:41.630 --> 00:31:42.910
Chuan isn't here.

00:31:43.750 --> 00:31:44.830
Is something wrong?

00:31:44.830 --> 00:31:46.370
Grandma, let me help you out first.

00:31:46.370 --> 00:31:48.080
We have some questions for you.

00:31:48.080 --> 00:31:48.480
Go in!

00:32:04.720 --> 00:32:05.510
It's okay.

00:32:05.880 --> 00:32:06.810
Don't be afraid.

00:32:07.260 --> 00:32:07.830
Grandma,

00:32:08.110 --> 00:32:09.350
I need to ask you something.

00:32:09.350 --> 00:32:11.610
How many days has Cao Jinchuan been back?

00:32:12.000 --> 00:32:13.860
Chuan has been back for a few days.

00:32:14.380 --> 00:32:16.210
He went out early this morning.

00:32:17.160 --> 00:32:19.320
I really don't know where he went.

