00:32:27.880 --> 00:32:29.640
It's nothing serious. Don't be afraid.

00:32:29.640 --> 00:32:30.350
Wenjing,

00:32:30.750 --> 00:32:31.480
come up here.

00:32:32.040 --> 00:32:32.970
Take care of her.

00:32:34.350 --> 00:32:35.750
Grandma, let me help you.

00:32:42.670 --> 00:32:44.600
There are about 200,000 yuan here.

00:32:44.840 --> 00:32:45.790
So he hasn't left.

00:32:45.790 --> 00:32:47.590
He just went out for a bit, right?

00:32:47.990 --> 00:32:48.770
Put everything back the way it was.

00:32:48.770 --> 00:32:49.450
Set up surveillance around the area.

00:32:49.450 --> 00:32:50.850
Wait for him to come back.

00:32:55.920 --> 00:32:56.480
Ken.

00:33:08.350 --> 00:33:09.210
What are you doing here?

00:33:09.210 --> 00:33:09.900
Nothing.

00:33:09.930 --> 00:33:11.390
I just came to check on you.

00:33:11.600 --> 00:33:13.400
Aren't you going to invite me in?

00:33:14.200 --> 00:33:15.510
Just say it here.

00:33:16.450 --> 00:33:17.250
How come...

00:33:17.280 --> 00:33:18.560
