00:33:19.950 --> 00:33:20.440
No.

00:33:20.440 --> 00:33:22.640
I've been thinking these past few days,

00:33:23.980 --> 00:33:25.410
and the more I think about it,
the more it feels wrong.

00:33:25.410 --> 00:33:26.040
What?

00:33:26.450 --> 00:33:28.450
Baocai died after taking your drug.

00:33:29.290 --> 00:33:31.220
I ran away entirely because of you.

00:33:31.620 --> 00:33:32.210
Right?

00:33:33.480 --> 00:33:34.520
So I came

00:33:34.970 --> 00:33:36.500
to ask for some travel expenses.

00:33:36.500 --> 00:33:38.300
That's not too much to ask, is it?

00:33:39.420 --> 00:33:39.940
Yes,

00:33:40.430 --> 00:33:41.480
I know it hasn't been easy.

00:33:41.480 --> 00:33:41.880
But,

00:33:42.200 --> 00:33:44.330
we already cleared this up last time.

00:33:44.660 --> 00:33:46.720
You were the one who took me to Baocai.

00:33:48.210 --> 00:33:48.960
I'm not blaming you.

00:33:48.960 --> 00:33:49.400
I really am not.

00:33:49.400 --> 00:33:50.070
I don't blame you.

00:33:50.070 --> 00:33:51.170
I really don't blame you.

00:33:51.170 --> 00:33:51.750
It's just that...

00:33:51.750 --> 00:33:53.410
I really can't help right now.

00:33:53.640 --> 00:33:54.440
But I...

00:33:54.440 --> 00:33:55.000
I want to help you,

00:33:55.000 --> 00:33:56.640
but I don't have any money.

00:33:56.730 --> 00:33:57.640
You sold that stuff,

00:33:57.640 --> 00:33:59.920
and you're telling me you've got no money?

00:33:59.920 --> 00:34:01.070
I didn't sell any—

00:34:01.090 --> 00:34:01.440
I swear.

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:01.960
I haven't sold...

00:34:01.960 --> 00:34:03.400
I didn't sell a single bit.

00:34:03.400 --> 00:34:04.810
I have nowhere to sell them.

00:34:04.810 --> 00:34:06.340
I can't turn them into cash.

00:34:06.720 --> 00:34:07.270
Well,

00:34:08.000 --> 00:34:08.920
that works too.

00:34:10.100 --> 00:34:11.449
I have a friend in Chunzhou

00:34:11.449 --> 00:34:13.710
who just happens to be looking for goods.

00:34:14.050 --> 00:34:15.909
Sounds a lot like what you've got.

00:34:16.440 --> 00:34:17.840
Hand the goods over to me.

00:34:23.100 --> 00:34:24.350
I don't have them at home.

00:34:24.350 --> 00:34:26.080
I was afraid to keep them there.

00:34:27.840 --> 00:34:28.920
I left them with a friend.

00:34:28.920 --> 00:34:29.550
I swear.

00:34:31.280 --> 00:34:34.280
I think you don't understand
the situation right now.

00:34:35.570 --> 00:34:37.489
I've got nothing to lose.

00:34:38.280 --> 00:34:39.560
I'll take you down with me if I have to.

00:34:39.560 --> 00:34:40.400
If I go to prison tomorrow,

00:34:40.400 --> 00:34:42.400
at least I'll have a place to retire.

00:34:43.880 --> 00:34:45.139
But you're different.

00:34:45.560 --> 00:34:46.800
You have a sick daughter, right?

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:47.710
I asked around.

00:34:47.710 --> 00:34:48.400
It's fine.

00:34:48.489 --> 00:34:49.420
I'm begging you.

00:34:49.550 --> 00:34:50.630
Please.

00:34:51.900 --> 00:34:53.170
My daughter is sick.

00:34:54.280 --> 00:34:55.409
It's not easy for me.

00:34:55.960 --> 00:34:56.940
I really struggle.

00:34:56.940 --> 00:34:57.480
I'm on my own,

00:34:57.480 --> 00:34:58.540
taking care of her.

00:34:58.590 --> 00:34:59.430
I was planning to

00:34:59.430 --> 00:35:01.020
sell those things

00:35:01.230 --> 00:35:02.710
to get money to save her.

00:35:03.950 --> 00:35:05.030
I need to cure her.

00:35:09.040 --> 00:35:09.850
Save her life?

00:35:12.300 --> 00:35:13.700
Who's going to save mine?

00:35:18.830 --> 00:35:19.870
If I go down,

00:35:21.320 --> 00:35:22.850
do you think you'll be okay?

00:35:24.560 --> 00:35:25.520
If you stay safe,

00:35:28.170 --> 00:35:29.300
she'll be safe.

00:35:33.120 --> 00:35:33.700
Right?

00:35:40.800 --> 00:35:41.440
Yes.

00:35:42.630 --> 00:35:43.320
Yes.

00:35:43.610 --> 00:35:44.260
Let's go.

00:35:52.850 --> 00:35:53.890
I lied to you.

00:35:54.880 --> 00:35:55.880
I hid the stuff...

00:36:00.590 --> 00:36:01.440
It's really,

00:36:02.800 --> 00:36:04.130
really behind that back

00:36:04.670 --> 00:36:05.400
pool.

00:38:34.730 --> 00:38:35.330
Go inside!

00:38:35.960 --> 00:38:36.560
Go inside!

00:39:20.800 --> 00:39:21.430
I'm sorry.

00:39:23.520 --> 00:39:24.380
I'm sorry. I...

00:39:28.480 --> 00:39:30.340
I shouldn't have let you see that.

00:39:31.300 --> 00:39:32.370
He was a bad man.

00:39:33.270 --> 00:39:34.470
He wanted to hurt you.

00:39:34.810 --> 00:39:35.960
I have to protect you.

00:39:35.960 --> 00:39:37.630
I can't let anyone hurt you.

00:39:42.320 --> 00:39:43.190
Listen to me,

00:39:43.590 --> 00:39:44.320
now...

00:39:45.400 --> 00:39:46.000
Now,

00:39:46.360 --> 00:39:47.720
stay in this room.

00:39:48.320 --> 00:39:49.380
Don't go anywhere.

00:39:49.510 --> 00:39:51.640
Don't come out no matter what you hear.

00:39:52.460 --> 00:39:54.660
I'll come back and open the door for you.

00:40:06.590 --> 00:40:07.280
I know.

00:40:16.400 --> 00:40:17.330
Don't be scared.

00:40:28.370 --> 00:40:29.300
Don't be scared.

00:41:21.520 --> 00:41:22.170
Xiaodong,

00:41:23.640 --> 00:41:25.100
come to my house right now.

00:41:25.950 --> 00:41:26.610
Right now.

00:41:42.680 --> 00:41:49.720
[Next Episode Preview]